.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

Food: mango, pineapple, cherry, broccoli, garlic
Nationality: british, danish, german, norwegian, swede
Beverage: beer, coffee, milk, tea, water
Flower: bellflower, rose, orchid, zinnia, amaryllis
City: new-york, paris, boston, hamburg, hannover
1. Nationality:british == Food:cherry
2. Nationality:swedish == City:boston
3. Nationality:danish == Beverage:tea
4. Food:pineapple is on the left of Food:broccoli
5. Food:pineapple == Beverage:coffee
6. Flower:orchid == City:paris
7. Food:garlic == Flower:rose
8. Beverage:milk is in the middle
9. Nationality:norwegian is on the far left
10. Flower:amaryllis is on the left or right of City:new-york
11. City:hannovers is on the left or right of Flower:rose
12. Flower:bellflower == Beverage:beer
13. Nationality:german == Flower:zinnia
14. Nationality:norwegian is on the left or right of Food:mango
15. Flower:amaryllis is on the left or right of Beverage:water

.:: Answer ::.
